{"tid":963010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2018年俄羅斯　史詩劇《成吉思沙皇》 中國自古屬於俄羅斯","createTime":"2018-12-31T09:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T16:31:59.000Z","uid":47714,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3884f16040b7edf1c99b38beeffe96b1e4b741d6","tid":963010,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:42:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/471177046343408/videos/724068047960339/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F471177046343408%2Fvideos%2F724068047960339%2F&d=cTAjkEOo76T5poMGkCYoaRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=fff99132\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/471177046343408/videos/724068047960339/</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年俄羅斯<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t92/1/16/1f1f7_1f1fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft92%2F1%2F16%2F1f1f7_1f1fa.png&h=f5888779&s={SIZE}\" />史詩劇《成吉思沙皇》<br />\n<br />\n中國：「台灣、西藏、新疆自古屬於中國」。<br />\n俄羅斯：「中國自古屬於俄羅斯」。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯現在已經認成吉思汗為俄羅斯的國家英雄。這就非常有意思了，因為歷史上蒙古<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t9f/1/16/1f1f2_1f1f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft9f%2F1%2F16%2F1f1f2_1f1f3.png&h=7eafebc3&s={SIZE}\" />從1240年開始統治俄羅斯，1279年開始統治中國<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tc6/1/16/1f1e8_1f1f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ftc6%2F1%2F16%2F1f1e8_1f1f3.png&h=7034bd3e&s={SIZE}\" />。也就是說，成吉思汗在成為中國的「元太祖聖武皇帝」之前，已經是俄羅斯的「成吉思沙皇(Чингис-царь)」長達40年。所以，成吉思汗的孫子忽必烈征服中國，就是俄羅斯沙皇的後代征服中國。<br />\n<br />\n因此按照中國人那套「新疆、西藏、台灣自古是中國神聖不可分割領土」的邏輯，俄羅斯官方應該宣布：「我們成吉思沙皇的後代們征服了中國，中國自古是俄羅斯神聖不可分割的領土」。<br />\n<br />\n衷心希望中國能夠早日回歸俄羅斯母親的懷抱，支持莫斯科武力收復中國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n內有片"},{"pid":"cf754ba3d941b9f1b82d725d77d94939f50327b4","tid":963010,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:44:43.000Z","msg":"被支那 被蛾人"},{"pid":"7c220227b1ca06c8f1e3c1cbc73bfb399a9b118c","tid":963010,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:48:33.000Z","msg":"根本蒙古先係最有資格講自古以來嗰個<br />\n幾時輪到你支狗俄狗喺度吱吱喳喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad73d83f3d7a331b2558d64af5cb696a050c29b","tid":963010,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:50:16.000Z","msg":"係咪等於宣戰？ 外交部靜晒既？"},{"pid":"fdcbff87623e416f99901d9bcaf8892ce523484a","tid":963010,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T16:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccad55529ded8897ed330f8f409428ef62258f5","tid":963010,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T16:30:44.000Z","msg":"自大唐開始<br />\n有邊個中原政權係中原漢族？"},{"pid":"6207bfa85660293a94cec2714e20231385457ad3","tid":963010,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T16:31:59.000Z","msg":"口交部：「.......」"}]}